::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502013201: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/F10202001_G52/Act502013201.json-->
::'''Ruoyue:''' Tsk, that can't be a good omen.
::'''Ruoyue:''' The Luofu has been ravaged by disaster recently. Everyone thinks that the Cloud Knights are capable of solving every problem under the sun, no matter how great or small.
::'''Ruoyue:''' But the Ambrosial Arbor's growth doesn't fall within the scope of operations for the Cloud Knights...
::'''Ruoyue:''' I'm not sure if the master diviner has foreseen this? I'm thinking, probably not.
